  <steps>
    <step order="1">Load all knowledge files. Read spec.md FR-12 (lines 159-164) + Owner Q&amp;A row on dispatch mechanism (line 340).</step>
    <step order="2">Verify MCP access to spaarkedev1 by running `mcp__dataverse__read_query` against `sprk_analysisaction` filtered to 1 row; confirm result returns successfully.</step>
